reviewText: This is a sad but very educative documentary!!! This takes you deep into the sad but realistic facts of the cruelties of the third reich. That is my opinion!!!

The seller did not send me the video he/she advertisted, the video I ordered, or the video that was listed on the packing slip.  There was a request on the packing slip that I try to contact him/her by email to resolve issues, if I had any before giving a negative review here.  I did that, and the seller did not respond.  I am stuck with a DVD I didn't order and a DVD that was different than advertised.  I am extremely disappointed, especially since the seller did not respond to my email, the email he/she requested I send before writing this. I WOULD NOT BUY FROM THIS SELLER AGAIN!
